<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ويؤكد بـ<span class="c1">"أجمع"</span> بعد <span class="c1">"كله"</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وبـ<span class="c1">"جمعاء"</span> بعد <span class="c1">"كلها"</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وبـ<span class="c1">"أجمعين"</span> بعد <span class="c1">"كلهم"</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وبـ<span class="c1">"جمع"</span> بعد <span class="c1">"كلهن"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وقد يغنى <span class="c1">"أجمع"</span> و<span class="c1">"جمعاء"</span> و<span class="c1">"أجمعون"</span> و<span class="c1">"جمع"</span>. عن <span class="c1">"كله"</span> و<span class="c1">"كلها"</span> و<span class="c1">"كلهم"</span> و<span class="c1">"كلهن"</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">وهذا معنى قولي:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>ودون <span class="c1">"كل"</span> قد يجيء <span class="c1">"أجمع"</span> .... . . . . . . . . . .<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وقد يجاء بعد <span class="c1">"أجمع"</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span> بـ<span class="c1">"أكتع"</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وبعد <span class="c1">"جمعاء"</span> بـ<span class="c1">"كتعاء"</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وبعد <span class="c1">"أجمعين"</span> بـ<span class="c1">"أكتعين"</span>.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وبعد <span class="c1">"جمع"</span> بـ<span class="c1">"كتع"</span>.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وقد يجاء بعد <span class="c1">"أكتع"</span> و<span class="c1">"كتعاء"</span> و<span class="c1">"أكتعين"</span> و<span class="c1">"كتع"</span>.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>بـ<span class="c1">"أبصع"</span> و<span class="c1">"بصعاء"</span> وأبصعين<span class="c1">" و"</span>بصع<span class="c1">".<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وزاد الكوفيون بعد "أبصع<span class="c1">" و"</span>بصعاء<span class="c1">" و"</span>أبصعين<span class="c1">" و"</span>بصع<span class="c1">": "</span>أبتع<span class="c1">" و"</span>بتعاء<span class="c1">" و "</span>أبتعين<span class="c1">" و"</span>بتع<span class="c1">".<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>ولا يجاء بـ"أكتع<span class="c1">" وأخواته -غالبا- إلا بعد "</span>أجمع".<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) هـ سقط "أجمع".</p> </div>